tool_description: The Craigslist API provides access to a wide range of classified advertisements, allowing you to search for and retrieve listings from various categories such as jobs, housing, services, and more.
name: Craigslist Data
title: Craigslist Data

api_list.name: Gigs
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://craigslist-data.p.rapidapi.com/gigs"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "craigslist-data.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
